<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
  <script src="https://ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/jquery/3.3.1/jquery.min.js"></script>
  <style>
    .even { color: red; }
  </style>
  <script>
  $(function() {
    $("li").each(function(index) {
      if (index % 2 == 0) {
        $(this).addClass("even");
      }
    });
  });
  </script>
</head>
<body>
  <h1>.each() 메소드</h1>
  <ul>
    <li>첫번째 아이템</li>
    <li>두번째 아이템</li>
    <li>세번째 아이템</li>
  </ul>
</body>
</html>